OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FA Sikh man accused of the murder of a
OL,8,Ffirst-year university student has told
OL,9,Fa court that he had acted in self-
OL,10,Fdefence after the teenager had
OL,11,Fracially abused him and knocked his
OL,12,Fhair out of his turban before grabbing
OL,13,Fit.
OL,15,FVickrum Digwa is on trial at
OL,16,FSouthampton Crown Court charged with
OL,17,Fthe murder of 18-year-old Henry Nowak,
OL,18,Ffrom Chafford Hundred, Essex, in
OL,19,FBelmont Road in Southampton, on
OL,20,FDecember 3 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
