PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779372669
OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FThe 23-year-old is also charged with
OL,8,Fcarrying a knife in public and his
OL,9,Fmother, Kiran Kaur, 53, is accused of
OL,10,Fassisting an offender by removing a
OL,11,Fweapon from the scene.
OL,13,FThe court has heard that Digwa was
OL,14,Fcarrying a kirpan ` a religious knife
OL,15,F` with a 21cm blade which the
OL,16,Fprosecution says caused five stab
OL,17,Fwounds to Mr Nowak, including two to
OL,18,Fthe back of his legs and a fatal wound
OL,19,Fto the chest.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
