FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779372669
OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FThe defendant told the court that he
OL,8,Fhad been walking near to his home when
OL,9,Fhe stepped on to the road when he saw
OL,10,FMr Nowak walking towards him, looking
OL,11,F"drunk", not walking in a straight
OL,12,Fline and "stumbling a little".
OL,14,FHe said that Mr Nowak then said to
OL,15,Fhim: "You could have moved up a little
OL,16,Fbit more."
OL,18,FDigwa said: "I then turned around and
OL,19,Fsaid 'You're right, I could have moved
OL,20,Fup, carry on with your day'.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@GO]tD@JOUtD@]O]wD@FOUxD@JO]zD@
OL,26,AMOU
