PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779372669
OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FI then said 'You're drunk, I am just
OL,8,Ftrying to get to my car, you're right,
OL,9,Fsorry'."
OL,11,FHe said he was saying stuff like 'I am
OL,12,Ffrom Essex, you do not know what
OL,13,Fpeople from Essex are on'."
OL,15,FDigwa said he felt that Mr Nowak was
OL,16,F"threatening" him and saying to him
OL,17,F'You think you're a bad boy' before Mr
OL,18,FNowak pulled out his phone to record
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,26,@qD@HOUuD@[O]xD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
