PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779372669
OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FHe said: "I was thinking in my mind
OL,8,Fhe's recording me and this has just
OL,9,Fescalated. During these months there
OL,10,Fhad been a lot of attacks on Sikhs and
OL,11,Fa lot of them had been videoed as well
OL,12,Fby the attackers."
OL,14,FDigwa said he then reached to block
OL,15,Fthe phone and grabbed it, which he
OL,16,Fsaid was followed by Mr Nowak punching
OL,17,Fhim because he wanted his phone back.
OL,19,FHe said that Mr Nowak then punched off
OL,20,Fhis turban and grabbed him by the
OL,21,Fhair, pulling him so he had bent over.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
