PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779372669
OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FDigwa said: "He started saying 'I am
OL,8,Fgoing to kill you'.
OL,10,F"I felt like that he was going to use
OL,11,Fmy kirpan on me."
OL,13,FHe said at this point he pulled his
OL,14,Fkirpan knife out of its sheath and
OL,15,Fstabbed Mr Nowak to the back of his
OL,16,Flegs but said he was not aware of Mr
OL,17,FNowak being stabbed in the chest.
OL,26,@oD@MOUsD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
