PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779372669
OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FThe defendant said it was at this
OL,8,Fpoint that his brother arrived which
OL,9,Fthen led to the emergency services
OL,10,Fbeing called.
OL,12,FWhen asked why he had not told police
OL,13,Fthat he had stabbed Mr Nowak, he said:
OL,14,F"I was scared, this is the first time
OL,15,Fanything like this had ever happened."
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
