PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779372669
OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FDigwa said that he had asked his
OL,8,Fmother, who along with his father
OL,9,Farrived at the scene, to hold his
OL,10,Fkirpan while he picked up his
OL,11,Freligious items which had fallen to
OL,12,Fthe ground during the incident.
OL,14,FThe prosecution has said that Kaur
OL,15,Ftook the kirpan back to the nearby
OL,16,Ffamily home where it was later found.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
