PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779372669
OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FDigwa said: "I felt abused, scared, it
OL,8,Fmade me feel a bit better that I had
OL,9,Fmy family there. My mind was fuzzy,
OL,10,Feverything went on so quickly, I
OL,11,Fcouldn't comprehend everything that
OL,12,Fwas going on."
OL,14,FHe added that the first time he was
OL,15,Faware that Mr Nowak had been stabbed
OL,16,Fin the chest was in his first police
OL,17,Finterview.
OL,26,@oD@MOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
