PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779372669
OL,3,CSikh man tells court he stabbed
OL,4,Cstudent in self-defence after he was
OL,5,C'abused'
OL,7,FDigwa said that he found out that Mr
OL,8,FNowak had died while in the police
OL,9,Fstation and said: "I cried, I was
OL,10,Fscared. I didn't mean to do it and I
OL,11,Fam sorry it happened."
OL,13,FThe defendants deny the charges and
OL,14,Fthe trial continues.
